        {*  MAGES *}
Mages are the elemental guild of Holy Mission.  Their magical power
comes from the study of elements.  Mage-Master Yorel is the
guild advisor, helping all mages learn their spells.  Mage-Master
Cherlindrea keeps the tower in prime shape, protecting the secrets
of the guild.

Guildmaster:  Saffrin
Asst. Guildmaster: Waldo
